ris-mom-vanessa-williams-joe-west-120160593/ |title='The Flash' Casts 'Candyman' Star as Iris Mom |last=Prudom |first=Laura |date=September 29, 2015 |website=Variety |access-date=September 29, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"S2ArrowCrossover\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/the-flash-recap-the-epic-arrow-crossover-begins-with-vandal-savage-two-hawks |title=\"THE FLASH\" RECAP: THE EPIC \"ARROW\" CROSSOVER BEGINS WITH VANDAL SAVAGE & TWO HAWKS |last=Gallaway |first=Lauren |date=December 1, 2015 |website=Comic Book Resources |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204063546/http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/the-flash-recap-the-epic-arrow-crossover-begins-with-vandal-savage-two-hawks |archive-date=December 4, 2015 |access-date=December 1, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Anderson\">{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2016/01/06/exclusive-arrows-diggle-to-help-the-flash-take-on-king-shark/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: Arrow's Diggle To Help The Flash Take On King Shark |last=Burlingame |first=Russ |date=January 6, 2016 |website=Comicbook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107162944/http://comicbook.com/2016/01/06/exclusive-arrows-diggle-to-help-the-flash-take-on-king-shark/ |archive-date=January 7, 2016 |access-date=January 7, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Barnes\">{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2015/08/25/exclusive-the-flash-casts-demore-barnes-as-firestorm-villain-tok/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: The Flash Casts Demore Barnes as Firestorm Villain Tokamak |last=Burlingame |first=Russ |date=August 25, 2015 |website=Comicbook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150827170433/http://comicbook.com/2015/08/25/exclusive-the-flash-casts-demore-barnes-as-firestorm-villain-tok |archive-date=August 27, 2015 |access-date=August 25, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Bell\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/the-flash-tone-bell-scott-evans-iris-editor-1201657834/ |title='The Flash' T