dy Mientus Returns as Pied Piper/Hartley in Season 2 |last=Gelman |first=Vlada |date=February 9, 2016 |website=TVLine |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115195026/http://tvline.com/2016/02/09/the-flash-pied-piper-returns-andy-mientus-season-2/ |archive-date=November 15, 2016 |access-date=November 7, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Paige\">{{Cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2016/01/26/the-flash-season-2-cast-female-speedster-allison-paige/ |title='The Flash' Season 2 Casts Female Speedster Trajectory \u2013 Allison Paige |last=Mitovich |first=Matt Webb |date=January 26, 2016 |website=TVLine |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129060251/http://tvline.com/2016/01/26/the-flash-season-2-cast-female-speedster-allison-paige/ |archive-date=January 29, 2016 |access-date=January 31, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Stafford\">{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2015/12/16/exclusive-geomancer-coming-to-the-flash/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: Geomancer Coming To The Flash |last=Burlingame |first=Russ |date=December 16, 2015 |website=ComicBook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151218003638/http://comicbook.com/2015/12/16/exclusive-geomancer-coming-to-the-flash/ |archive-date=December 18, 2015 |access-date=December 16, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sutherland\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/listings/20160407cw03/ |title=(#219) \"Back to Normal\" |website=The Futon Critic |access-date=April 8, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Turton\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/the-flash-of-two-worlds-9-new-images-from-the-flash-season-2-episode-2 |title=\"The Flash of Two Worlds\": 9 new images from \"The Flash\" Season 2, Episode 2 |last=Ching |first=Albert |date=October 2, 2015 |website=Comic Book Resources |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004095010/http://www.comicbookresources.com/article/the-flash-of-two-worlds-9-new-images-from-the-flash-season-2-episode-2 |