egory:Lutheranism| ]]\n[[Category:1517 in Christianity]]\n[[Category:16th-century introductions]]\n[[Category:16th-century neologisms]]\n[[Category:Christian terminology]]\n", "name_user": "67.60.129.213", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lutheranism"}
